!! Search for tiddlers modified or created in so many days

<div id=bd>

```
# Modified in the last 7 days
[all[tiddlers]!is[system]days:modified[-7]]

# Modified between 40 days and 300 days
[all[tiddlers]!is[system]days:created[-300]!days:created[-40]]
```

</div>

